&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; Very good point about acceptance testing and system boundaries. I
&gt; hadn&#39;t
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; thought of this and people often forget to mention it. Of course, this
&gt; &gt;&gt; has a
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; great effect on the tools you end up using.
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt;
