&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; neccessary.
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; Thanks for the distinction you made between integration tests and
&gt; larger
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; scale ones. I think I understand a little better where the boundaries
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; lie
